1.title: A Blindy Date (Pilot)

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

1.plot: Two guys who move from Jersey settle in their new home in Venice, CA. Robby comes home after hustling and gets a blind date. Andy gets one by doing nothing. It's at the same place. Same time. What could go wrong?

2.title: The Man Band

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

2.plot: The boys come up with an idea for some serious cash. Well, it was good 20 years ago, at least they're trying. Watch as they try to revive a wonderful, magical anomaly of music past.

3.title: U-Tube?

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

3.plot: Robby has another "brilliant" idea to make the boys some money. YouTube. Andy doesn't know what that is and decides to get some food. Andy gets jumped. Robby tries to sing again. Oy. Vey.

4.title: Fundy-Raiser

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

4.plot: The boys are coming to the end of their welfare. Robby comes up with a last minute idea to help them get a nice sum of money. Andy drinks a lot. Cops are involved. Surprise.

5.title: Serving Time

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

5.plot: Well...well...well...it finally had to happen. One of the boys cracked and thru some miraculous circumstances...got a job. I know. Unreal right?. We'll see how long that lasts. And the other takes advantage of the situation. Cheers.

6.title: Benched at a Park

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

6.plot: After a crazy night of celebrating, Robby wakes up and wants some coffee. Andy is not there. Nope. He is lost and Robby doesn't really care. Guess Andy should just google it.

7.title: Feelin' Kinda Sunday

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

7.plot: OK...this one's a bit...wild. The boys abandon any plan to make some money because they want to drink. Yup. They want to drink hard. Cheers.

8.title: Mantees

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

8.plot: Robby needs some help and he found a sale just in time. Andy does Robby a favor, but he ends up screwing himself. Oh yea. There's Pokemon Go. players everywhere...everywhere...and police.

9.title: The Sumo Band

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

9.plot: Robby has realized that Andy is the one slowing him down in his attempts to make that green. He plans to prove this in an epic battle of the bands competition. Who will be the champion?

10.title: The First Date

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

10.plot: Well the glorious day is here. Robby finally gets to go on a date with Michelley. Hooray to the world...oh wait...does he really? Tune in to discover what may be a date Robby won't forget. And Andy gets way too involved in a sci-fi film.

11.title: The Pasta Shop

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

11.plot: Andy apparently is one Hell of a cook. Robby is too wasted to clean up the house so Andy decides to cook him a great meal to inspire him. And boy did he. Be careful not to share too many secrets around the old microwave.

12.title: It Hits the Fanny Pack

episode of.title: The Andy and Robby Show (TV Mini-Series 2014– )

12.plot: Spring cleaning has hit the boys and as they clean, Robby finds his sweet pack. They decide to hit up Venice Beach to see what they can fit in the new sweet pack. Andy gets drunk. Robby gets mad. It's a typical trip to the beach.

imdb.plot outline: Andy and Robby are two best friends and lovable idiots from New Jersey. They decide to move out to Venice, California in hopes of jump starting anything to make themselves happy and some cash. Unfortunately, they moved during a bad economic recession. Without much "traditional education" they take it upon themselves to create schemes and other money making ideas in hope of making enough for rent without getting traditional jobs? Will they make it? Will they get lucky? Or get drunk and fail. Time will tell.
